headline: Union Pacific (UNP): Reassessing Valuation After a Recent Share Price Rebound
summary: Union Pacific (UNP) has quietly pushed higher over the past month, with the stock up about 7%, as investors reassess rail volumes, pricing power, and what that means for longer term earnings. See our latest analysis for Union Pacific. Zooming out, that recent 7.4% one month share price return has only nudged Union Pacific to a 3.6% year to date share price gain.
